snippet.title: Pond Scum Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Steam PCVR:
https://store.steampowered.com/app/2617030/Pond_Scum_A_Gothic_Swamp_Tale/
Meta Quest:
https://www.meta.com/experiences/24648126204801675/

At the edge of the Deep Swamp stands Snappy and his gang.
Anxious to proceed they press on as a rite of passage for all young pond dwellers. What will they find ahead?

Uncover the secrets of the swamp in this Diorama-based VR Platformer.
